閱讀、不傳閱，例如李怡、練乙錚、泛民左膠；中立的或投機的，在選舉時期惡意攻擊的，例如王岸然，不予理會，偶然閱讀，但不傳閱。<br />\n此外，我方目前必須全面撤離社運。空出主場予共匪左膠泛民。焦土政策。<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：戰敗第一件事，要做什麼？清黨。勝利不能清黨，戰敗反而可以順利清黨。將叛徒點名批鬥，掃地出門。清黨猶如出教（ex-communication），永遠不許回來。<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：趕鬼入豬群。堅持批鬥，將盧斯達這群人趕到泛民左膠陣營去。<br />\n<br />\n以上果d 算唔算清算？盧斯達又算唔算？"},{"pid":"007f0345eeed47aa950fed72858905c394fc2dd0","tid":52824,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kV0T4mN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkV0T4mN.jpg&h=1359e47c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcOH17J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcOH17J.jpg&h=e32d1de9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a5ecb60807c1c5ce67d3da1cd872f538c02643","tid":52824,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kV0T4mN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkV0T4mN.jpg&h=1359e47c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcOH17J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcOH17J.jpg&h=e32d1de9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />清算不算清算..清算!陳國師的事，能算清算麼？"},{"pid":"9212b025387b65bbae7f3bffacd8290b4e758980","tid":52824,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T06:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kV0T4mN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkV0T4mN.jpg&h=1359e47c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcOH17J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcOH17J.jpg&h=e32d1de9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/